  ('eba8bb4b-5313-47ae-b3c1-dc23d6f9037d', 'demo-navigation-user', 'ChatGPT Caricature', 'chatgpt-caricature', 'AI Caricature Generator - Turn Photos into Fun Cartoon Portraits', 'ChatGPT Caricature is an AI-powered caricature generator that transforms your photos into fun, personalized cartoon portraits. Join the viral AI caricature trend that&#x27;s taking over social media in 2026.

Key Features

6 Unique Caricature Styles: Choose from Classic Caricature, Job Caricature, 3D Cartoon, Comic Style, Chibi, and Pop Art styles

Personalization Options: Add your job title, hobbies, and personality traits to create truly unique portraits

Fast Generation: Get your high-quality caricature in seconds, no design skills required

No ChatGPT Plus Needed: Unlike using ChatGPT directly, no subscription or prompt engineering required

High-Resolution Downloads: Download crisp, high-quality images perfect for social media or printing

What Makes It Special

Professional-grade AI caricature engine with advanced face recognition

Create viral &quot;me and my job&quot; caricatures with profession-specific props and themes

Privacy-first approach - your photos are processed securely

Perfect for social media profiles, gifts, merchandise, or just for fun

How It Works

Upload a clear face photo

Choose your preferred caricature style

Optionally add job, hobbies, and personality details

Download your personalized cartoon portrait in seconds

Perfect for creating shareable content for Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, and WhatsApp.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772713556079-cgzpvm.jpg', 'https://chatgptcaricature.pro/', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772713559657-cnspep.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', TRUE, FALSE, '["0196c2b1-da65-4c1b-9a9d-10e274a88377"]', '2026-03-05T12:26:01.112Z', '2026-04-03T15:25:53.390Z'),
  ('989f999c-6c16-4cfc-a27d-0a0a0a4a943f', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Homebase Flights', 'homebase-flights', 'Cheap flights from your airport. Save up to 90%', 'Homebase Flights is a flight deal alert service that solves one frustrating problem: getting amazing deal alerts from airports you don&#x27;t live near.

Unlike other flight deal services that send deals from 5-10 different cities, Homebase Flights focuses exclusively on YOUR home airport. You pick one airport, and every deal we send departs from there.

Our system monitors flight prices daily and uses AI to curate only the best deals worth your attention. Members typically save $500+ per flight compared to regular prices.

The service includes a money-back guarantee: if you don&#x27;t save at least 3x the subscription cost within a year, you get a full refund.

Perfect for travelers who are tired of seeing &quot;NYC to Paris $289!&quot; when they live in Denver.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772713548633-7m2yp8.jpg', 'https://homebaseflights.com', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772713551030-arwhrs.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', TRUE, FALSE, '["53df6e96-e03b-4533-ba17-afbe29eca5fc","6504ccb4-f903-41f0-93ea-6f7081c62a17"]', '2026-03-05T12:25:52.627Z', '2026-03-06T15:09:55.025Z'),
  ('ca40c785-cbd0-4aa3-9341-d0ee57ea7906', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Seedream 5.0 AI', 'seedream-50-ai', 'Unleash stunning AI-generated images with Seedream 5.0 – photorealism &amp; creativity at your fingertips.', 'Introducing Seedream 5.0 AI, the fifth-generation diffusion transformer model revolutionizing image generation for creators, designers, and businesses. This cutting-edge AI empowers you to effortlessly create stunning, photorealistic images from text descriptions, opening up a world of creative possibilities previously unimaginable. We&#x27;re thrilled to announce a limited-time New Year Sale offering 50% off – don&#x27;t miss this opportunity to elevate your visual content!

Seedream 5.0 AI excels in generating high-quality images up to 2K resolution, boasting unprecedented prompt comprehension and creative versatility. Whether you need captivating product photography, compelling character designs, intricate concept art, or breathtaking landscapes, Seedream 5.0 AI delivers exceptional results. Its advanced features include multi-subject composition, allowing you to create scenes with three or more distinct subjects that maintain their individual attributes and natural spatial relationships. Furthermore, Seedream 5.0 AI provides granular style control, enabling you to instantly switch between photorealism, anime, cyberpunk, watercolor, oil painting, and 3D styles – all controlled via intuitive text prompts or reference images.

The benefits of using Seedream 5.0 AI are numerous. It empowers creators to produce professional-grade images in seconds, significantly accelerating workflows. Its exceptional prompt comprehension ensures accurate interpretation of complex prompts, including spatial relationships, lighting, and style modifiers, resulting in images that perfectly match your vision. The ability to generate scenes with multiple subjects maintains individual attributes and natural interactions, addressing a common limitation of other image generators. The instant switching between various styles and the high-quality output at 2K resolution make Seedream 5.0 AI an indispensable tool for a wide range of applications.

Seedream 5.0 AI is designed for ease of use. Simply enter your prompt, configure the settings, and generate – no design experience is required. We offer flexible subscription plans to suit your needs, from hobbyist-friendly options to enterprise-level solutions with priority support. Our pricing structure includes pay-as-you-go options and monthly/yearly subscriptions, with yearly plans offering significant savings.

Thousands of creators trust Seedream 5.0 AI for its ability to deliver studio-quality image generation. Users rave about the prompt comprehension, noting its ability to rival professional photography. The tool is essential for character designs, environment art, and promotional materials, offering a comprehensive solution for various creative needs. The image-to-image editing feature is particularly praised for its precision and ability to seamlessly apply style transfers, object removals, and background replacements.

