  ('8ecd9556-a1a8-4c84-9421-99eddba21fad', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Seedance 2.0', 'seedance-20-7737', 'Multi-shot AI video generator with reference, keyframe &amp; voice control', 'What is Seedance 2.0?
