  ('265033ff-5a68-469a-8db4-b32285300d95', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Directories.Best', 'directoriesbest', 'A curated hub of niche directories that helps businesses earn credibility listings without wasting time on low quality mass submissions.', 'Directories.Best is a curated hub that helps businesses, founders, agencies, and marketers discover and evaluate higher-quality web directories across multiple niches. Instead of pushing “submit everywhere” tactics, it promotes a smarter approach: treat directories as credibility placements that support trust, discovery, and consistent brand signals.

The problem it solves
Most directory strategies fail because people mass-submit to random sites, end up on low-value pages, and waste time maintaining inconsistent listings. It becomes noise, not SEO. Directories.Best gives you a cleaner starting point by organizing directory options into a network you can actually review and choose from, based on relevance and fit.

What makes it special

Curated network: A focused collection of directory properties, not an endless unvetted list.

Niche and category coverage: Find directory options that align with specific industries and audiences.

Quality-first workflow: Encourages selective submissions that improve trust signals and reduce clutter.

