  ('a7da45e8-5c99-4b6e-b11d-2c3d125c8273', 'demo-navigation-user', 'LeakedPrompts - #1 AI Prompts Library', 'leakedprompts-1-ai-prompts-library', 'Save, Edit, and Manage Best AI Prompts in one place.', 'I did not plan to build a prompts tool.

