IndexTTS-2 Online is designed for creators, indie developers and small teams who want cutting-edge speech synthesis quality without building their own TTS infrastructure.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772711996537-40yywh.jpg', 'https://indextts-2.com', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772711998476-i0j59q.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', TRUE, FALSE, '["68c47817-8733-4488-aef5-d01708647206","53df6e96-e03b-4533-ba17-afbe29eca5fc"]', '2026-03-05T12:00:00.465Z', '2026-03-06T15:01:43.025Z'),
