  ('cbd8b050-89e9-48cc-9c00-2b6ef1981e28', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Sora-2-AI', 'sora-2-ai', 'Transform Text into Stunning Videos in Seconds', 'Sora 2 AI is a next-generation text-to-video studio that turns written ideas into cinematic clips in seconds, closing the gap between imagination and high-end motion production. Traditional video pipelines demand storyboarding, camera crews, editing suites, and weeks of iteration; Sora 2 AI compresses that workflow into a browser experience where creators simply describe scenes. Marketing teams rapidly draft campaign cuts, educators craft illustrative explainers, indie filmmakers prototype shots, and social-media managers keep feeds fresh—without hiring specialist talent for each iteration.

