  ('1e5c9c8d-b389-449a-8815-626d02a007c5', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Pro Batch Resizer', 'pro-batch-resizer', 'Privacy-first online multiple image resizer with pre-build 130+ smart presets', 'ProBatchResizer is a high-performance web utility built for creators, marketers, and developers who need to process images at scale without compromising privacy.

Why use ProBatchResizer?

