  ('47393aac-33fe-465a-848c-faafc663d0c0', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Bitcoin Profit Calculator', 'bitcoin-profit-calculator', 'Calculate your BTC trading profits and ROI instantly with real-time exchange rates', 'BTCProfitCalculator.com is a practical decision-making tool designed for people who want to understand Bitcoin investment results using data, not hype.

