  ('c6ce9d8c-f5e0-437c-9304-7e242684673e', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Gnizdo', 'gnizdo', 'Keep stock, prices, and orders aligned across WooCommerce, Etsy, eBay, and Shopify', 'GNIZDO — Multichannel Inventory Coordination for Ecommerce Sellers
GNIZDO is a web-based coordination layer designed for ecommerce sellers who operate across multiple sales channels and need a reliable single source of truth.

Modern ecommerce doesn’t fail because of marketing or UX — it fails because inventory, prices, and orders drift out of sync. Overselling, refunds, marketplace penalties, manual spreadsheet fixes, and constant dashboard hopping become daily routine. GNIZDO exists to stop this before it happens.

GNIZDO focuses on four core platforms: WooCommerce, Etsy, eBay, and Shopify. Instead of trying to support everything, it goes deep on these channels to deliver accuracy, clarity, and operational calm.

What GNIZDO does

Keeps inventory, prices, and orders aligned across all connected platforms

Detects data drift and conflicts automatically

Surfaces oversell risks before orders break

Provides daily checks instead of reactive firefighting

Gives sellers a clear, unified view of their operational reality

How it’s different
GNIZDO is not another overloaded “all-in-one” dashboard.
It is a coordination and early-warning system built for real operational workflows.

Modern 2026-level interface focused on clarity, not noise

Drift detection instead of blind syncing

Risk visibility instead of post-fact refunds

Lightweight AI assistance for analysis and explanations — not gimmicks

Who it’s for
GNIZDO is built for small and mid-sized ecommerce sellers who:

Sell on more than one platform

Are tired of manual reconciliation and spreadsheet gymnastics

Want proactive control instead of constant damage control

GNIZDO helps sellers move from reactive chaos to calm, predictable operations — so inventory decisions are made with confidence, not guesswork.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772707038870-hcrywu.jpg', 'https://gnizdo.space', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772707040467-0ocepv.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', TRUE, FALSE, '["70a88584-1a0a-48fb-ab02-72f6c46aef3f","68458d43-0483-480b-9c69-9b20ea80d411","79dcfd2b-0388-48c6-a04b-81e9c077e49e"]', '2026-03-05T10:37:21.451Z', '2026-03-06T14:49:35.567Z'),
