  ('a9ce8bdc-72ac-493e-ad7d-40359e5fbf02', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Junting Orbit', 'junting-orbit', 'Stop wasting hours on job posts that aren’t right. Junting Orbit reads the JD, tells you whether to apply or skip, and helps you move fast with confidence.', 'Junting Orbit is a job-hunt copilot built for people who want to apply smarter, faster, and with way less mental clutter.

Instead of reading long job descriptions line by line and guessing whether a role is worth your time, Junting Orbit reads the job post for you and turns it into a clear decision: Apply immediately, Tailor &amp; apply, or Skip for now. It also explains why by surfacing key requirements, signals, and the red flags and green flags for you in that specific role. No fluff, no vague advice, just clarity.

When you decide to move forward, Junting Orbit helps you act quickly. It can generate a role-specific cover letter and tailor your resume based on the job description and your existing resume. Because it remembers your profile history and what you’ve used before, outputs stay consistent across applications instead of feeling random every time.

The other pain point it solves is the one nobody talks about until it hurts: interview prep. Junting Orbit saves each analyzed job into a tracker, including the job description and exactly which resume and cover letter you used. So when an interview invite comes in days or weeks later, you can instantly refresh your memory and show up prepared, without digging through old files and tabs.

It works directly on major job sites (LinkedIn, Indeed, Seek, and The Hub) through the Chrome extension, and the dashboard gives you a clean place to manage everything: a Kanban board for your pipeline, calendar view, a Resume Hub with ATS-compatible templates and a resume builder, and a LinkedIn Profile Optimizer that scans your profile and suggests improvements.

In short: Junting Orbit turns job hunting from “overwhelming and messy” into a repeatable system you can actually stick to.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772706895177-vmedg4.jpg', 'https://junting-orbit.com', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772706896324-bd5cjb.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', TRUE, FALSE, '["53df6e96-e03b-4533-ba17-afbe29eca5fc","68458d43-0483-480b-9c69-9b20ea80d411","89496dee-703b-4598-afde-30a447401f77"]', '2026-03-05T10:34:57.205Z', '2026-03-06T14:48:47.226Z'),
