  ('b929bd31-99de-4357-89db-e44f0682cd1c', 'demo-navigation-user', 'ImageUnblur', 'imageunblur', 'Restore blurry photos with AI in seconds', 'What does it do? Image Unblur is an AI-powered online tool designed to restore clarity to low-quality images. It automatically analyzes and sharpens blurry photos, removes pixelation, and upscales resolution. Whether you need to fix out-of-focus shots, make blurry text readable, or restore old damaged photos, it handles the complex processing in seconds to deliver crisp, high-definition results.

