  ('fa3cdb38-9491-4ebb-909e-b68d3af93955', 'demo-navigation-user', 'UGC Maker', 'ugc-maker', 'UGC Maker: Create Viral UGC Ad Videos with AI in Minutes', 'UGC Maker – Create Authentic UGC Ad Videos with AI

UGC Maker is a next-generation AI video platform that transforms any product link, text, or creative idea into authentic, high-converting UGC-style videos — all without cameras, actors, or editors. With UGC Maker, you can generate human-like, relatable videos that look and feel like real user content in just a few minutes.

