  ('947d4e44-99ec-4a0d-9507-2ff4dee66a9b', 'demo-navigation-user', 'AI color sorter machine', 'ai-color-sorter-machine', 'JIACUI AI Intelligent Color Sorter: A precision machine integrating High-Resolution Optical Sensing Technology and Deep Learning (DL) AI Algorithms.', 'It thoroughly transcends the limitations of traditional sorters that rely solely on color differences, enabling multi-dimensional, stereoscopic intelligent recognition and judgment of material color, shape, size, texture, and even material differences, much like the human eye and brain.** This series (including AI Chute Type and AI Belt Type) utilizes a highly efficient image acquisition system and powerful AI computing to rapidly remove tiny impurities from agricultural products (such as moldy grains, insect-damaged items, discolored particles, stones, and glass) and foreign objects/defective items from industrial materials. It is committed to providing customers with ultra-high sorting accuracy and stability of up to 99.9%, establishing itself as an intelligent expert for quality upgrading, cost reduction, and efficiency improvement in global agricultural processing, food safety, and industrial recycling sectors.

