  ('5d89a5c6-53a6-47bc-822d-d424580da15f', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Pixora', 'pixora', 'Turn phone photos into studio-quality product images in 60 seconds. No prompts, no editing skills needed.', 'Pixora – AI Product Photography Platform

Product photography is expensive. A single professional shoot costs $1,700 or more. Small brands face an impossible choice: pay thousands for quality visuals or use DIY photos that kill conversions.

