Fashion, beauty, electronics, food, jewelry, furniture—Pixora supports every product category. Ghost mannequin effects for apparel. Macro texture shots for cosmetics. Virtual staging for real estate. One platform covers all visual needs.

Pricing That Makes Sense

Start free with 100 credits. Pro plan costs $9.90/month for 2,000 credits with full commercial license. Replace a $5,000 studio day with unlimited AI-generated variations.

Your product photos directly impact conversion rates. 75% of shoppers rely on images to make purchase decisions. Poor visuals mean lost sales. Pixora gives every brand access to professional-quality photography—without the professional price tag.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772706498965-r6w755.jpg', 'https://www.usepixora.com', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772706500570-sp38g3.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', TRUE, FALSE, '["988aa262-7be8-4cce-a181-c709d8d100f0","53df6e96-e03b-4533-ba17-afbe29eca5fc","efe9065d-6594-441f-9df9-e62042ccbe46"]', '2026-03-05T10:28:21.410Z', '2026-03-06T14:44:07.534Z'),
