  ('4a5d9b7a-9865-47a1-9aca-ccc5dd5f1203', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Assindo', 'assindo', 'AI agent that makes real phone calls, searches the web, posts to social media, and handles tasks for you. No setup, no self-hosting. Available on iOS, Android,', 'What is Assindo?
Assindo is a managed AI agent that works in the real world. Unlike chatbots that only generate text, Assindo takes action - it makes actual phone calls, navigates IVR menus, waits on hold, and talks to real people on your behalf.

What problems does it solve?

