Task overload: Assindo searches the web, posts to social media, schedules future tasks, screens incoming calls, and executes code - all from a single chat interface.

Self-hosting complexity: Unlike open-source AI agents like OpenClaw that require Docker, API keys, and dedicated servers, Assindo requires zero technical setup. Each user gets a dedicated AI server in the cloud.

Key Features

