29 languages supported across 21 countries', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772703363739-eqtw3t.jpg', 'https://dofollow.tools/product/assindo', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772713474838-jd5o4c.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', FALSE, FALSE, '[]', '2026-03-05T09:36:06.037Z', '2026-03-06T15:09:26.332Z'),
  ('b318fd84-b878-4d6d-9a62-6909c6d70a8d', 'demo-navigation-user', 'ChurnWard', 'churnward-1996', 'Stop losing SaaS revenue to failed payments. Automated dunning, expiring card alerts, win-back campaigns, and revenue analytics in one tool.', 'Failed payments are silently killing your MRR.

