You can be up and running in under 10 minutes and most founders cover the monthly subscription fee by recovering just one or two payments.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772703360827-1ifcc5.jpg', 'https://dofollow.tools/product/churnward-1996', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772713575716-lqg2z8.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', FALSE, FALSE, '[]', '2026-03-05T09:36:01.651Z', '2026-03-06T15:10:02.910Z'),
  ('0f6f1f82-5da1-4d87-8fe3-4f5dffd7ac35', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Kaomojiya', 'kaomojiya', 'Japanese kaomoji &amp; text emoticons — browse by category, one-click copy ٩(◕‿◕｡)۶', 'What is Kaomojiya?
Kaomojiya is a free, comprehensive online collection of Japanese kaomoji and text emoticons. Unlike standard emoji that render differently across platforms and devices, kaomoji are crafted entirely from Unicode text characters — meaning they display identically everywhere, on any device, any app, and any platform without compatibility issues.

With thousands of carefully curated kaomoji organized across dozens of emotion categories, Kaomojiya is the ultimate resource for anyone who wants to add personality and expressiveness to their digital communication.

The Problem Kaomojiya Solves
Standard emoji are limited. They look different on iPhone vs Android, they lack nuance, and they often feel generic. Meanwhile, the world of Japanese kaomoji offers incredible depth of expression — but finding quality kaomoji has traditionally been frustrating. Most existing kaomoji websites are cluttered with ads, contain outdated collections, lack proper categorization, or force users through annoying popups and sign-up walls.

Kaomojiya was built to change that. It provides a clean, fast, ad-light experience where you can instantly find and copy the perfect kaomoji for any emotion or situation.

Key Features

Thousands of kaomoji across dozens of categories — From cute and happy to angry, sad, surprised, love, confused, sleepy, and everything in between. Each category is carefully curated with dozens of unique variations.

One-click copy to clipboard — Simply click or tap any kaomoji to instantly copy it. No selecting text, no right-clicking, no extra steps. Just click and paste wherever you want.

Universal compatibility — Because kaomoji are plain Unicode text, they work perfectly in every app: LINE, Discord, X, Instagram, Facebook, iMessage, WhatsApp, Slack, Telegram, Reddit, email, and more.

Multilingual interface — Available in three languages: English, Japanese, and Chinese, making Kaomojiya accessible to users worldwide.

Mobile-first responsive design — Browse and copy kaomoji effortlessly on your smartphone, tablet, or desktop. The interface adapts perfectly to any screen size.

No account required — Start using Kaomojiya immediately. No sign-up, no email verification, no login walls. Completely free and instantly accessible.

Subcategory filtering — Within each emotion category, kaomoji are organized into subcategories (basic, cute, sparkle, decorated) so you can quickly narrow down to the style you want.

Blazing-fast page loads — Built with modern web technology for enterprise-grade performance. Pages load in milliseconds.

Popular Categories
Here is a taste of what you will find on Kaomojiya:

Happy and Joy: Cheerful expressions for celebrating good moments

Sad and Crying: Emotional faces for when words are not enough

Love and Hearts: Romantic and affectionate emoticons

Angry and Frustrated: Expressive faces for venting frustration

Cute and Kawaii: Adorable faces that melt hearts

Greeting and Goodbye: Waving and farewell emoticons

Apologetic: Sorry and remorseful expressions

Sleepy and Tired: Drowsy faces for late-night chats

Animals (Cat, Bear, Rabbit): Cute animal-themed kaomoji

Sparkle and Magic: Dazzling and mystical expressions

Shrug and Confused: Perfect for uncertain moments

And many more including niche categories like muscle, bald, sunglasses, throwing, magic, and dozens of others.

Who Uses Kaomojiya?

Social media enthusiasts who want their posts to stand out with unique text expressions

Content creators and streamers looking for creative text decorations

Discord, LINE, and chat app power users who love expressive text emoticons

Japanese culture fans who appreciate the artistry behind kaomoji

Writers and bloggers who want to add warmth and personality to their articles

Customer support teams who use friendly kaomoji to create warmer interactions

Students and professionals who brighten their messages with a personal touch

Anyone who wants to go beyond generic emoji and express themselves creatively

How It Works

Visit kaomojiya.org

Browse emotion categories or use the navigation

Click or tap any kaomoji to copy it to your clipboard

Paste it into any message, post, comment, or document

No downloads, no browser extensions, no app installations, no fees.

