  ('b800095a-5ea4-4513-9f05-cb0d50b31a0d', 'demo-navigation-user', 'Ruumix', 'ruumix', 'The Design-to-Shopping Interior AI Agent', 'Here is a highly compressed, punchy English version, perfect for a landing page, pitch deck, or quick read.

Ruumix: The Shoppable AI Design Engine
The Core Concept
Ruumix is an AI platform that bridges the gap between inspiration and transaction. It transforms user-uploaded room photos into stunning interior designs where every item is real, in-stock, and clickable.

Who It’s For

For Consumers: An instant AI interior designer. Upload a photo, chat to refine the style, and shop the look immediately.

For Brands: A visual sales engine. Upload your catalog, and Ruumix generates designs using exclusively your inventory—converting browsing into buying.

Why Ruumix Wins (The 4 Key Differentiators)
1. No &quot;Hallucinations&quot; – Real Shoppable Products
Unlike generic AI (e.g., Midjourney) that invents fake furniture, Ruumix generates real products. Every sofa and lamp comes with a &quot;Buy Now&quot; tag. We don’t just show a style; we sell the solution.

2. Brand-Specific Inventory Engine
A game-changer for retailers. Ruumix can be &quot;locked&quot; to a specific brand’s catalog. If a retailer uses Ruumix, the AI creates designs using 100% their products, ensuring zero competitor exposure and maximum conversion.

3. Conversational Editing
Design isn&#x27;t a one-shot process. Ruumix allows users to refine results via natural chat (e.g., &quot;Make it more modern&quot; or &quot;Change the rug to blue&quot;), making the experience interactive and precise.

4. Structural Integrity
We respect the architecture. Ruumix keeps the walls, windows, and floors exactly where they are, ensuring the design is physically possible, not just artistically pleasing.

In Short
Midjourney is for art. Ruumix is for commerce.
We turn empty rooms into full shopping carts.', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772707184819-itnbsp.jpg', 'https://www.ruumix.ai', 'https://img-navigation.995010.xyz/uploads/2026-03-05/1772707193040-d79sot.jpg', 'Free', NULL, NULL, 'live', FALSE, TRUE, '["0196c2b1-da65-4c1b-9a9d-10e274a88377","53df6e96-e03b-4533-ba17-afbe29eca5fc","efe9065d-6594-441f-9df9-e62042ccbe46"]', '2026-03-04T09:54:30.751Z', '2026-03-06T14:50:41.029Z'),
